---
import { Markdown } from 'astro/components';
const setbackText = `
## Current Project - Setback

Setback is an innovative new multiplayer shooter where you donâ€™t kill your opponents.
Instead they are rewinded back a few seconds to a previous location.

Players can choose from a variety of different weapons and special consumables.
There is a high focus on character mobility with several movement mechanics that can be utilized to move swiftly through the arena.
The various game modes (Race, Safe Zone and Capture the Flag etc.) are designed around the fact that being rewinded in time is a disadvantage.
We hope Setback will provide a thrilling and engaging experience for those who love fast-paced shooters.

Setback is currently available for wishlisting on Steam. You can also sign up to participate in upcoming playtests!
`;
---

<div class="games">
  <span id="games" class="nav-anchor" />
  <div class="content">
    <div class="desc">
      <Markdown content={setbackText} />
    </div>
    <!-- <div class="steam-card">
      <iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1119780/" frameborder="0" width="646" height="190"></iframe>
    </div> -->
    <div class="steam-card-small">
      <div class="steam-icon">
        <svg><use href="icons.svg#steam" /></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="wishlist-btn">
        <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1119780/Setback/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="Setback on Steam">Setback on Steam</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .games {
    width: 100%;
    background-image: url("/setback-background.webp");
    background-color: rgb(80, 80, 80);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-blend-mode: multiply;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #111;
  }

  .games h1, h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: white;
  }

  .games p {
    color: #ddd;
  }

  .content {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .desc {
    margin: 2rem;
  }

  .steam-card {
    max-width: 500px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .steam-card-small {
    margin: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    min-width: 320px;
    fill: #acafb9;
    flex-direction: column;
    background-color: #282e39;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 5px rgba(1, 1, 1, 0.8);
    /* display: none; */
  }

  .steam-icon {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 160px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .wishlist-btn {
    margin: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(111, 167, 32) 5%, rgb(88, 138, 27) 95%);
  }

  .wishlist-btn:hover {
    background: linear-gradient( to right, #8ed629 5%, #6aa621 95%);
  }

  .wishlist-btn a {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .content {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .steam-card-small {
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .steam-icon {
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .desc {
      margin-left: 1rem;
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }

    .steam-card {
      display: none;
    }

    .steam-card-small {
      display: flex;
    }
  }
</style>
